85
00:04:01,337 --> 00:04:03,170
Do what?

86
00:04:03,172 --> 00:04:06,374
Choosing a new laptop is
an incredibly personal ritual.

87
00:04:06,376 --> 00:04:07,742
You have taken away

88
00:04:07,744 --> 00:04:10,611
weeks of agonizing thought,
tedious research,

89
00:04:10,613 --> 00:04:13,981
sleepless nights filled
with indecision. I j...

90
